title: GET_VEHICLE_NUMBER_PLATE_TEXT_INDEX

0xF11BC2DD9A3E71950x499747B6// GetVehicleNumberPlateTextIndex
int GET_VEHICLE_NUMBER_PLATE_TEXT_INDEX(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to get the plate index ofReturns: Returns the plate index, reference eVehiclePlateIndiciesenum eVehiclePlateIndicies {
	SanAndreasCursive = 0,
	SanAndreasBlack = 1,
	SanAndreasBlue = 2,
	SanAndreasPlain = 3,
	SRExcept = 4,
	NorthYankton = 5,
	// All indicies below this require b3095
	ECola = 6,
	LasVenturas = 7,
	LiberyCity = 8,
	LSCarMeet = 9,
	LSPanic = 10,
	LSPounders = 11,
	Sprunk = 12,
}
codeBlocks:
local vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsIn(PlayerPedId(), false)
-- Example usage for GET_VEHICLE_NUMBER_PLATE_TEXT_INDEX
GetVehicleNumberPlateTextIndex(vehicle)
